<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Split Sheet Entry Removed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .percentage-box {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Split Sheet Entry Removed</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
      
      <p>We're writing to inform you that your entry in the split sheet for the song <strong>"{{songTitle}}"</strong> has been removed by the song owner.</p>
      
      <div class="percentage-box">
        <p><strong>Your previous allocation:</strong> {{oldPercentage}}%</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>This means you will no longer receive royalty payments for this song. If you had an active claim on this split, it has been invalidated.</p>
      
      <p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>You are no longer entitled to royalties from this song</li>
        <li>Any pending or active splits for this song have been removed</li>
        <li>This change was made by the song owner</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>If you believe this removal was made in error or if you have any questions about this change, please contact the song owner directly or reach out to our support team.</p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@ratedafrika.com">support@ratedafrika.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you,<br/>The ratedAfrika Team</p>
      <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@ratedafrika.com">support@ratedafrika.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 